HB 606 Original 2026 Regular Session Bourriaque
Abstract: Provides for definitions, operations, and regulations for personal delivery
devices.
Present law defines "agent", "business", "nonpedestrian area", "pedestrian area", and
"personal delivery device" as used in present law.
Proposed law clarifies definitions for "nonpedestrian area", "pedestrian area", and "personal
delivery device".
Present law specifies that the operation of a personal delivery device is governed by present
law and Federal Aviation Admin. airport regulations.
